- Persist event stream to a file
- Persist repositories into database
- Link dependent records with aggregate root
- Fold entity state over events
- Build a minimal message board
  Modeled on lobste.rs
    GET /recent Paginated list of stories by posting date
    GET /stories/new Form to post a new story
    POST /stories Create a new story
    GET /stories/:id View a story and comments
    POST /comments Add a comment to a story
    GET /users/new Form to create a new user
    POST /users Create a new user
    GET /users/:id View posts by user
